    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Eternal Bonds</i> 是一款解谜平台游戏，你需要在两个角色的视角之间切换，在飞船中解谜。你和你那奇特的搭档能逃出飞船，还是会永远被困在解谜中？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039320/extras/0deff830b121330ec24a1884dcc5ab8a.avif?t=1771344087\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039320/extras/639a2e708fe7abbeea10a20975985041.poster.avif?t=1771344087\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039320/extras/639a2e708fe7abbeea10a20975985041.webm?t=1771344087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039320/extras/639a2e708fe7abbeea10a20975985041.mp4?t=1771344087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特点</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款小型单人游戏（游戏时长取决于你的聪明程度）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过在两个角色的视角之间切换来解决谜题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演宇航员和他的机器人，他们分别困在一艘废弃飞船的不同部分</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拉动杠杆、按下按钮、使用传送门等，帮助他们到达出口门</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个令人兴奋的故事</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039320/extras/df4ffa9a0a1e242d1cd8bfccb135fae8.avif?t=1771344087\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><table><tr><td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039320/extras/f603d9bf8d46d9f7276b50dafa092134.poster.avif?t=1771344087\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039320/extras/f603d9bf8d46d9f7276b50dafa092134.webm?t=1771344087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039320/extras/f603d9bf8d46d9f7276b50dafa092134.mp4?t=1771344087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></td><td><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039320/extras/97abacc37de7881b33c82c44896a4335.poster.avif?t=1771344087\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039320/extras/97abacc37de7881b33c82c44896a4335.webm?t=1771344087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039320/extras/97abacc37de7881b33c82c44896a4335.mp4?t=1771344087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏由Castical制作。通过YouTube关注开发进度！</p>",
